should make a counterproposal.

246
00:13:14,213 --> 00:13:16,884
Go through this draft, point by point.

247
00:13:16,967 --> 00:13:19,179
Be crystal clear about what you want.

248
00:13:19,262 --> 00:13:21,598
Yeah. Yeah, that's good.

249
00:13:21,681 --> 00:13:25,520
