under these circumstances.

253
00:13:38,411 --> 00:13:42,542
Oh, I figured you'd want this back.

254
00:13:42,626 --> 00:13:44,711
Yes. Thank you.

255
00:13:45,378 --> 00:13:46,505
Can I ask?

256
00:13:47,256 --> 00:13:49,176
