into filming <i>The Wedding Night</i>

259
00:13:53,431 --> 00:13:55,308
when I first got to New York.

260
00:13:55,391 --> 00:13:56,894
I was young and naïve,

261
00:13:56,977 --> 00:14:00,607
and fell in love with a fink
who steered me wrong.

262
00:14:00,690 --> 00:14:04,237
