every copy I could find.

263
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:05,697
Thought I got them all.

264
00:14:06,198 --> 00:14:08,575
Well, how did you get into burlesque?

265
00:14:08,659 --> 00:14:11,496
It's funny.
Um, I auditioned for the Rockettes,

266
00:14:11,579 --> 00:14:13,082
but I wasn't tall enough.

267
00:14:13,165 --> 00:14:18,881
