perform at the <i>Ziegfeld Follies</i>

268
00:14:18,965 --> 00:14:21,551
and I thought, "That is what I wanna do."

269
00:14:21,634 --> 00:14:24,471
And whatever you might think
about burlesque,

270
00:14:24,555 --> 00:14:26,182
