272
00:14:31,564 --> 00:14:32,983
So you don't have to worry.

273
00:14:33,066 --> 00:14:35,443
I wanted to tell you that, face-to-face.

274
00:14:35,528 --> 00:14:37,989
I'm so happy for you, Polly, really.

275
00:14:38,907 --> 00:14:42,119
And to be perfectly honest,

276
00:14:42,203 --> 00:14:47,126
I did a little burlesque show of my own.

277
00:14:47,209 --> 00:14:49,671
Just for one person. Archie.

278
00:14:49,754 --> 00:14:51,172
Archie from next door?

279
00:14:51,256 --> 00:14:52,550
In our windows.

280
00:14:53,175 --> 00:14:54,927
Well, you always were sweet on him.

281
00:14:57,055 --> 00:15:01,019
