about which postures you mean?

427
00:23:33,726 --> 00:23:37,481
Um, Sister, uh, perhaps you and the doctor

428
00:23:37,564 --> 00:23:41,069
could demonstrate for us numbskulls?

429
00:23:41,152 --> 00:23:42,153
Buffoons.

430
00:23:42,237 --> 00:23:43,656
What about this item?

431
00:23:43,739 --> 00:23:46,283
